snippet.title: Octavia's Anthem - Console Highlight Video
snippet.description:
Octavia's Anthem is live on PlayStation 4 and Xbox One!

Force your foes to face the music with Lotus’ newest warrior, Octavia. Dominate your enemies with new weapons, journey for Octavia in a new Quest, create incredible images with the new Captura mode and much more. Download and play it now for free!
https://www.warframe.com
